@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_luircs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(0.89)
    tmp = 0.85
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.exp(tmp))
    v2 = (v0 * (0.44 / (v2 + 0.26 / tmp + 0.87)))
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.61) - (v0 + 0.19 + v0 + 0.72)) * ((tmp + 0.93 * v2 + 0.99) * (v1 + 0.78 / tmp + 0.03)))
    data[tid] = v0
